    Scope and Contents
Work/Culture/Society Program Records, 1970-1981 include minutes, agenda, memoranda, correspondence, coordinator's files, faculty evaluations, homesteading materials, newsletters,  program review task force and self- study files, reports, statements, committee files, program notes, course materials, program reviews, schedules, research and print out materials.  
  
